{"tid":1329843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟歷史性第一次制裁香港","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:58:23.000Z","uid":65328,"like":200,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"88d76fcc3d05e7a0b09711624daad7290f84c95d","tid":1329843,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"反修例爭議在海外也持續發酵。歐洲議會通過議案，促暫停向香港出口或違人權的「人群管制裝備」。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會今日就香港反修例引發的一連串風波舉行辯論，議程包括是否促請歐盟委員會及歐盟對外事務部制訂措施，停止向香港出口「人群管制裝備」 及其他香港警方所使用的「非致命性武器」。這會是1997年香港回歸以來，歐洲議會首次針對香港提出制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2404537?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2404537%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAytUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=a71c2483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2404537?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"fe8c67ae60ea9f59107244afd4666250a03bd2ae","tid":1329843,"uid":78769,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"促請咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed9e79842b1c3cddd3f9503e5f8bc349f32e49b","tid":1329843,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"98de2756075d19a8a82f047704e96148379a61f7","tid":1329843,"uid":15654,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"促請呀 死標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cad17cebb075ff206196fc557a75eff5cd03352","tid":1329843,"uid":95487,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"以及對4名年輕示威者喪生致深切哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街，歐盟都識表示深切哀悼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭我dllm"},{"pid":"49293018a23912ba0c364dc132007d2bb6e0009c","tid":1329843,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cad17cebb075ff206196fc557a75eff5cd03352","tid":1329843,"uid":95487,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"r